{"data":[{"id":564614968,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b031debe9a4c54df77a3c60012ce1ec3","url_token":"pei-yan-lin-93","name":"林哥","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ace3669b322b82678f2061d7aa2b9443_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ace3669b322b82678f2061d7aa2b9443_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b031debe9a4c54df77a3c60012ce1ec3","user_type":"people","headline":"国家安危公安系于一半","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":4313,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564614968","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546399968,"updated_time":1546412213,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":10,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"disallowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e这个回答告诉我们：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003e这世界，从来不缺少指出错误的人\u003cbr\u003e唯独缺少面对未知勇于给出自己答案的人\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e经过一众网友的这番嘲弄，怕是世间又少了一个后者\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e犯错不可怕，实际上99%的变革者都是失败者，而成功者99%的想法也是错误的，哪怕开国伟人也在犯错。但正是1%的成功者的1%的正确的答案，推动了这个世界的发展。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们都读过高中，我们都知道哥德巴赫猜想，但我们其中有多少人认真思考并试图证明它，又有多少人得到证明结果后哪怕知道它99%是错的还去勇敢地公开它。究竟多少人，有给出自己答案的勇气？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个少年没有证明出来哥德巴赫猜想一点不丢人，以他高中生的修为犯一些数学上的低级错误也不丢人。但他给出他的答案的勇气值得肯定，他承认自己错误的态度值得肯定。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e假如全中国每个高中生本科生乃至研究生，都思考一下这个问题，然后给出自己的“错误”，这无数的创意和经验可能会给那些站在金字塔顶端的数学家提供很多灵感，搞不好一个恍惚间就有人证出来了。我们需要99%的错误啊，这无疑是有利于数学的进步的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e固然，少年在这件事的处理上还显得很浮躁、狂妄和自大，像极了我们每个人的少年时。志不轻狂妄少年，对这些我们应该一笑而过，继续鼓励少年们的“轻狂”，而不是嘲弄或打击。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我希望少年在经历这次错误后，还会纠正错误继续思考，不断完善自己的解法。而不是畏惧犯错，从此止步不前，知道哥德巴赫可是数学王冠上的明珠啊，我一个高中生肯定解不出来，我再也不在这上浪费时间了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎是个理性的社区，希望大家不要纠结于一个高中生的小挫败，你要想证明自己的强大不妨公开你的解法，或者给那些试图给出解法的人一些鼓励。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"这个回答告诉我们：这世界，从来不缺少指出错误的人 唯独缺少面对未知勇于给出自己答案的人经过一众网友的这番嘲弄，怕是世间又少了一个后者犯错不可怕，实际上99%的变革者都是失败者，而成功者99%的想法也是错误的，哪怕开国伟人也在犯错。但正是1%的成功…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=452\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_cou